      </h2>
      <p>Premium subscribers pay ₹49.9/month for daily WhatsApp market reports. By subscribing you agree to:</p>
      <ul style="margin: 12px 0 12px 24px;">
        <li>Monthly manual renewal required</li>
        <li>No automatic billing or auto-debit</li>
        <li>No refunds once report has been delivered</li>
        <li>Service may be discontinued with 7 days notice</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
        5. Newsletter
      </h2>
      <p>By subscribing to our newsletter you agree to receive daily market summary emails. You can unsubscribe at any time by contacting theclosereportdaily@gmail.com.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
        6. Intellectual Property
