      <p>All content on TheCloseReport including reports, formatting and design is owned by TheCloseReport. You may not reproduce or redistribute our content without permission.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
