      </h2>
      <p>TheCloseReport shall not be liable for any financial losses or damages arising from use of information on this site. Use of this service is entirely at your own risk.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
        8. Changes to Terms
      </h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to update these terms at any time. Continued use of the service after changes constitutes acceptance of new terms.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
        9. Contact
      </h2>
      <p>For any questions about these terms, contact us at theclosereportdaily@gmail.com</p>

    </div>
  </div>
